{"tid":2015972,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"沒有建制派下區議會還是走建制派的路","createTime":"2020-05-14T05:10:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-17T13:48:43.000Z","uid":47194,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f5d24616324c18ce123e274b7dfb1714aafac261","tid":2015972,"uid":47194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T05:10:54.000Z","msg":"在五月十二日的黃大仙區議會上有兩個討論發言，一個是譚香文議員提出「鑽石山綜合發展計劃」（FBI）天橋，另一個是劉珈汶議員的「樂富事件」，前者質問的對象是房署，後者當然是警方了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，可是譚香文說不到十分鐘就被主席許錦成打斷，準備了的PowerPoint也不用了，相信大部份人都不知道譚說什麼，房署官員也沒有回應，因沒有入題就被腰斬了，根本不明你說什麼！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟後論到劉珈汶議員的「樂富事件」，奇怪是警方代表沒「走人」，乖乖的在席聽討論，但問題太複雜，七嘴八舌後時間不夠，劉珈汶要求追加時間，許主席卻不容，要討論到時即止，結果討論成了「斷截禾蟲」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，實際上留意政圈的人都會知道，黃大仙區議會在有關「反修例風波」積極性，跟別的區議會是雲泥之別，好像根本沒有做過什麼？觀中西區等早群情洶湧。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n過去區議會由建制主導，泛民派議員無論發言、提案等經常被主席拒絕、或中途打斷，直接或間接為政府部門保駕護航， 但現在照理黃大仙區會已是全泛民控制，正副市席都是泛民的<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，現任主席是民協的許錦成，但讓人見到的是行事與歷屆建制主導的無分別，把譚的討論中途腰斬，劉的不許加時，竟然出現在一個泛民主導的區議會上，由一個泛民派的主席執行，難怪警方代表不離席，房署代表不驚慌，原來是「會上有人好做事」，哈哈哈！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cec951a5b9e15547366a3b7e1b514d7a934f9b2","tid":2015972,"uid":125502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T05:11:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NkRzx1A.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FNkRzx1A.gif&h=65e3b426&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">見到連鄺俊宇自己都保唔住，你仲相信「溫柔是最大的勇武嗎？」</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">取消功能組別 五大訴求 缺一不可</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">全民習武 唯一出路</span></strong></span></div>"},{"pid":"191137aa06d002a13c517bd7f2391dd068f1405c","tid":2015972,"uid":77717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T05:16:01.000Z","msg":"咁撚唔團結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fe7bc6aaafb83614690e375e735a5a99d2393ac","tid":2015972,"uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T05:21:30.000Z","msg":"果個發展計劃應該要傾啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdea1cabf353a6f164f1da40a3ecb374d112e1cd","tid":2015972,"uid":57035,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T05:24:55.000Z","msg":"分化撚收皮啦 借啲移話議會冇用"},{"pid":"4119acfad060ccd265ad0f06dbaec78f8d78a13f","tid":2015972,"uid":19726,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T05:33:17.000Z","msg":"分化撚 拉"},{"pid":"e4829864a61b59911d0433e04de06507c792badf","tid":2015972,"uid":124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T06:52:44.000Z","msg":"區議會班友仔真係撚屌<br />\n會內分化又唔做野"},{"pid":"f02d849c3e0f2a4b9de14b5a8c5a5a27fbe197fa","tid":2015972,"uid":269732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T03:10:13.000Z","msg":"似係譚香文出post"},{"pid":"242bedc3dfe2324e888dad6bb6bf73d4a8d60818","tid":2015972,"uid":272840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f02d849c3e0f2a4b9de14b5a8c5a5a27fbe197fa","tid":2015972,"uid":269732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T03:10:13.000Z","msg":"似係譚香文出post"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T05:01:29.000Z","msg":"中出洋子嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cccd8b99aa2c677088407be0c4f346148a537ad8","tid":2015972,"uid":204031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T13:48:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">係FB1，唔係FBI</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr18-19/chinese/panels/hg/papers/hg20190506cb1-962-3-c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr18-19%2Fchinese%2Fpanels%2Fhg%2Fpapers%2Fhg20190506cb1-962-3-c.pdf&d=xUEPa7L8eIFrsai6sDUjHMtxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=dae09625\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr18-19/chinese/panels/hg/papers/hg20190506cb1-962-3-c.pdf</a><br />\n呢份文件第4頁第5頁<br />\n熟熟地果邊路嘅人都知<br />\n條天橋隔離係有條隧道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有扶手電梯，有升降機，24小時通行，仲要連鑽石山站<br />\n條天橋FB1根本係無用，只係Cap水工程<br />\n我估譚香文想屌呢樣野"}]}